<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-973] Allow DB2 JCC driver to work with Informix database</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-973</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Openjpa parses the DatabaseMetaData retrieved from the jdbc connection to determine the database type. For informix, if db2jcc driver is used, the product name in the DatabaseMetaData does not start with &quot;informix&quot;, but with &quot;ids&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12416593">OPENJPA-973</key>
            <summary>Allow DB2 JCC driver to work with Informix database</summary>
